==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wing-shell
<hw>Wing"-shell`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>Any one of various species of marine bivalve shells
belonging to the genus <gen>Avicula</gen>, in which the hinge border
projects like a wing.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>Any marine gastropod shell
of the genus <gen>Strombus</gen>. See <er>Strombus</er>.</def>
<sd>(c)</sd> <def>Any pteropod shell.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wingy</ent>⟦br⟧
